Approach
trim() method = removes any leading or trailing whitespace from the string.

Complexity
Time complexity: O(n)
Space complexity: O(1)

Code
class Solution {
    public int lengthOfLastWord(String s) {
        int wordStart =0;
        int count =0;
        s = s.trim();
        for(int i=s.length()-1;i>=0;i--){
            if(s.charAt(i)==' '){
                wordStart = i+1;
                break;
            }
            else if (i == 0) {
                wordStart = 0;
            }  
        }
        for(int i=wordStart;i<s.length();i++){
            count++;
        }
        return count;
    }
}
